   NCR Corp. and Teradata Corp., completing terms of a
venture for jointly developing their parallel-processing
computer technologies, said NCR bought 1,400,995 newly issued
Teradata shares for $26.26 each, or $36.8 million.
   The purchase gives Dayton, Ohio-based NCR, an
